<td headers="Type" class="gt_row gt_left">Multiple selection</td>
<td headers="Mandatory" class="gt_row gt_left">Yes. Provide at least one option</td></tr>
    <tr><td headers="Variable" class="gt_row gt_left">ProjectLeadingOrganization</td>
