                  or as general as 'Protozoa' (e.g., 'Plasmodium relictum', 'Toxoplasma gondii')</td>
<td headers="Type" class="gt_row gt_left">Multiple selection</td>
<td headers="Mandatory" class="gt_row gt_left">No</td></tr>
    <tr><td headers="Variable" class="gt_row gt_left">=ProjectFungiHazard</td>
<td headers="Label" class="gt_row gt_left">Fungi</td>
<td headers="Definition" class="gt_row gt_left">The fungi of interest for the Project. It can be as specific as a strain/serovar/etc of a species
