      than 'Event'?'. Grouping can be physical (e.g., parcel) or temporal (e.g., month)</td>
<td headers="Type" class="gt_row gt_left">Boolean</td>
<td headers="Mandatory" class="gt_row gt_left">Yes</td></tr>
